## Description {#details}

Iterator for the <code><a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/sandboxir/use">Use</a></code> edges of a <a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/sandboxir/value">Value</a>&#39;s users.

\\Returns a <code><a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/sandboxir/use">Use</a></code> when dereferenced.
